snippet.title: Copperfields Gameplay Trailer - Demo Release
snippet.description:
Our adventure platformer inspired by Limbo and Rain World is finally out on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2578740/Copperfields/?utm_source=Youtube&utm_medium=Demo&utm_campaign=Demo

Explore the garden of Copperfields, solve puzzles, gather gear and survive!
